{
  "texts": [
    "Entities like the IAEA offer platforms for international cooperation and standard setting.",
    "With AI development transcending national borders, the establishment of international safety standards and cooperative structures has become increasingly important.",
    "Engage in discussions and supervision focused on public safety.",
    "Just as IAEA's regulatory standards are periodically reviewed per the details of international action plans, the participation and feedback from civil society ensure the efficacy and appropriateness of regulations.",
    "promote inter-country collaboration and continual regulatory updates."
  ]
}